Cell.Text: [S] G|Oh, yes, partner! Let us be on our way.

Node.Caption: EL_BeginQuestAlignmentFD2Continue5: Well. Shall we go see how the old place has fared over all this time, partner?

Cell.Text: [S] This is essentially a dream I pushed into your mind. I needed to distract you while my soul gem bound itself to you. | Your response to my "damsel in distress" dream was a pleasant surprise. It's a shame I had to interrupt you. | I'm looking forward to seeing what you do when you have a beautiful woman at your mercy, and hours to play with her.

Node.Caption: EL_BeginQuestAlignmentFD2Continue4: What do you mean "Wake up"? I am awake!

Cell.Text: Excellent! | Now, before we begin the search, we need a safe and discrete place to use as a base. | I have the perfect place in mind. It's my old lair. It's well defended by magic, and I've never had a victim escape from it. | Once you wake up, I'll guide you there.

Node.Caption: EL_BeginQuestAlignmentFD2Continue3: Hmmm .... 'mutual interests', eh? Sounds like a like an interesting proposition.

Cell.Text: Our interests are aligned, and we both gain from this partnership. | I have many decades of experience, and I'm the most powerful mage of my generation. I specialized in healing both the body and the mind. | You are a powerful mortal with a great deal of potential. | So, it is to my own advantage to find a new body and invite you to join me in pursuit of our mutual ... interests.

Node.Caption: EL_BeginQuestAlignmentFG2Continue2: How can I be sure of that?

Cell.Text: It's simple. Demonstrate your worth to me. Prove that I'm better off with you as a partner than as a victim.

Node.Caption: EL_BeginQuestAlignmentFG2Continue1: How do I know you won't do so anytime you want?

Cell.Text: I do hope you understand the need for that little demonstration, | and I assure you, I will not take control unless you make it necessary.
